title: WiiWare NTSC-U Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles My Life As A Kin
description:
Name: Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles: My Life As A King
Platform: Wii/WiiWare
Released: May 12 2008
Format: NTSC




The USA WiiWare release of FFCC:MLAAK, a fantasy city management game that you just cant put down!

To install this you will need the Twilight Hack ( http://wiibrew.org/index.php?title=Twilight_Hack ) and WAD Installer on your wii.

Note: Yes this is a Re-Up from demonoid, if you don&#039;t like that then find the game somewhere else.
